            <lg xml:id="TK141">
<l>piṟaṉporuḷāṭ peṭṭoḻukum pētaimai ñālat</l>
<l>taṟamporuḷ kaṇṭārka ṇil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The folly of desiring her who is the property of another, is never seen</l>
<l>among those who see what's good and good for them on Earth.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
